      <title>特朗普胜选后，CFTC 的 Pham 谈美国加密货币监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/cftc-s-pham-on-us-crypto-regulations-after-trump-victory-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商品期货交易委员会委员 Caroline Pham 谈论唐纳德·特朗普在美国大选中取得压倒性胜利后的美国加密货币政策。她在“新加坡金融科技节”间隙与 Avril Hong 在“与 Haslinda Amin 的见解”节目中进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/cftc-s-pham-on-us-crypto-regulations-after-trump-victory-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:02:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>6500 亿欧元外流是德国政治动荡的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨领导的分裂联盟难以阻止大规模的资本流失，而唐纳德·特朗普连任后，资本流失可能会加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国农业部哈夫迈斯特谈中美贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/usda-s-hafemeister-on-us-china-trade-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国农业部贸易和外国农业事务代理副部长 Jason Hafemeister 讨论了中国关税以及该政策对两国的影响。他还指出印度是美国产品销售的未来合作伙伴。Hafemeister 在独家采访中接受了彭博电视台的 Stephen Engle 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/usda-s-hafemeister-on-us-china-trade-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:48:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激政策希望抵消特朗普风险 中国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-stocks-bounce-back-on-policy-hopes-promising-trade-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的出口数据和对更多政策刺激的希望超过了对唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统可能带来的贸易摩擦的担忧，中国股市从周三的下跌中强势反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-stocks-bounce-back-on-policy-hopes-promising-trade-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安赛乐米塔尔呼吁采取贸易措施应对中国出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/arcelormittal-says-market-unsustainable-but-sees-demand-pick-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安赛乐米塔尔公司呼吁采取更强有力的贸易措施来应对中国钢铁出口的大量涌入，该公司表示，这些出口导致市场难以为继，欧洲钢铁价格远低于边际成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/arcelormittal-says-market-unsustainable-but-sees-demand-pick-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国的威胁让股市交易员看好印度和日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-s-china-threat-has-investors-favoring-india-japan-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关税风险笼罩着中国资产，唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利将改变亚洲三大股票市场的短期资金流向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-s-china-threat-has-investors-favoring-india-japan-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡特朗普的影响，大选震动后油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡唐纳德·特朗普的大选胜利对原油市场可能产生的影响，油价在周三经历了过山车式波动后小幅走高，美元在选举后飙升后有所停顿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员考虑特朗普胜选和美联储，股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者为唐纳德·特朗普第二次当选总统以及美联储预期的降息做准备，亚洲股市跟随欧洲和美国股指期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选引发市场分歧，日本股市因盈利而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/japanese-stock-futures-gain-as-yen-extends-loss-on-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受企业盈利强劲和股票回购的推动，日本东证指数上涨。唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统选举中获胜提振了金融股，推高了该指数，但拖累了半导体相关股，拖累日经 225 指数下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/japanese-stock-futures-gain-as-yen-extends-loss-on-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贷方称没有美元支付系统将无法为非洲节省 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/no-dollar-payment-system-to-save-africa-5-billion-lender-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲大陆最大银行非洲及离岸地区商业银行业务主管表示，如果支付系统能够取消非洲跨境交易中的美元，则可以为非洲节省高达 50 亿美元的处理成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/no-dollar-payment-system-to-save-africa-5-billion-lender-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
